“The Mind is a TERRIBLE master , but a WONDERFUL servant “🔥

You have the power within you .. to Master control of your mind … and use it to change your outcomes .

It’s time to start using our minds to help us achieve and receive what we WANT not what we don’t want.

Our children are watching and determining what they believe is possible for themselves , based on what you believe is possible for you 🙏🏼

If you need guidance , I’ll show you how on Nov 11 at my event AWAKEN (link in bio for seats)

Watch this Video till the end to see how I used the power of Visualization to help my son @aaronkingsleymorel Experience an Awesome moment of personal achievement

node.text:
Why do you think shows like the bachelor don’t work ? Why do you think JLO keeps breaking up ? ( sorry 😬)

You can’t force “FINDING” , and you can’t neglect healing . 
Truth is : the only thing there is to find … is YOU

It’s you… you’re the one and your special someone is waiting on you to Heal and discover YOU…: your HEART ❤️ 

ITS TIME ….

To heal the thing that makes you NEED someone ✨
To heal the wounds that have the walls up around you heart ✨
To heal the pain … that keeps attracting partners with the opposite matching  pain ✨ ( read that again )
To finally learn accept and FEEL in your heart how wonderful and perfect you are … BEFORE anyone told you or made you feel any different .

Do that and honestly … you won’t “NEED” anyone … for you would have discovered your true soulmate .

It’s YOU ….. it’s YOU …. It’s time to focus on healing and discovering YOU .

Once you do that , and you trust in God , your heart will Open and you’ll attract to yourself like a magnet the person that most matches …. The person you’ve become ✨

When we don’t go IN and HEAL we keep attracting our WOUND , for the WOUND doesn’t want to be alone , alone is scary for the wound because Alone means you either Look outside for temporary comfort … or you go INSIDE and heal . The Wound doesn’t want to Heal, because it doesn’t want to FEEL ( read that again) 

If we give ourselves the space and time to heal …. 

The space and time to discover 
Your energy , your heart , your Love …. That’s what you’ll attract … 

Your heart will do what a dating app could never do , for you’ll be tapping into something more powerful than the mind of man …

You’ll be tapping into the power that connects us all 
The source of all love 
The power …. Of the healed heart ❤️

node.text:
This was me … this was the program I was running … it was one based on a deep rooted feeling of shame … and I had no idea it was there .

I went to the gym DAILY worked hard , real HARD yet nothing would happen … nothing would change . Till I realized I had to deal with the underlying EMOTION that was causing the issue … that’s when the weight magically appeared , when the internal happiness  was allowed to BE

Thing is I’m not alone … for this story is also your story , and your story is also mine .

See we all have deep rooted emotions that haven’t been dealt with that lead to programs that stop us from our true potential .

The “ I can’t be successful “ program 
The “ I always find a way to be in debt “ program
The “ I can’t find Love “ program 
The “ Im not worthy “ program 

Im happy to say that we’ve now helped hundreds unravel their limiting programming … by going underneath it … and discovering the underlying emotion that was never dealt with .

You too can deal with it … better yet , you can heal it … and that’s your journey , it’s all of our journey .

To unravel the fear based program and uncover the truth … the Light that lives within each of us .

If you’d like help , and you’re ready to go In and uncover your own limiting program … click the link in my bio and join myself and a couple thousand of your brothers and sisters whom all are ready to AWAKEN their highest potential on Nov 11-13 

I’ll see you there !

YOU have the ability to change your life ! It’s inside you ... it always has been since the day you were born .

Yet the traumas of your childhood and past have caused you to forget how incredible you are .

On this weeks episode I interview my brother @johnj.Rios as he shares his EXTRAORDINARY story of transformation . A story of a normal person just like you who was finally ready to begin his Journey to Higher Self 

From healing his body to growing his business the reality is his story is the stuff of movies! Yet it’s also your story ... it’s also possible for You!

Go right now to DannyMorel.com/podcast (link in bio) and listen to this weeks story of hope and transformation !

P.S Please be gracious with the typo :)

node.text:
If you’re going through tough times ... I pray this video brings you hope ... for this is our true story 

Claudia and I were about to have our son @micahmorel7 ... and I had lost EVERYTHING.

I was down to earning $900 a month , was living with my mother with a wife a son and one on the way , Couldn’t afford rent , couldn’t afford ... Food ... nothing .

I was in Mexico trying to build an MLM business when I received her call , they towed away her car at 8 months pregnant ... as she was at the store and I couldn’t do ANYTHING about it 

Talk about ROCK BOTTOM .

Yet we didn’t give up , we kept trying , kept searching within for any ounce of resolve possible ... one year later I even had to borrow $500 to host My sons first birthday 🤦🏻‍♂️

But our belief started paying off ! 

- I was able to start earning enough to afford Our own place 
- Then I was able to pay back creditors
- Then we bought a home 
- Then we built a company based on helping others grow !
- Finally , last November we sold that company and will never have to worry about a car being repossessed again 🙏🏼

I pray this video touches your heart and reminds you to never give up , no matter how tough it gets .

Remember ... everything you need , to fullfill everything you’ve always dreamed of ... has always been inside of you.. since the moment you were born 🙏🏼

Look forward to seeing YOU See in 2 weeks at AWAKEN !!!

P.S @iamclaudialorena4 @micahmorel7 I love you!

node.text:
Drop a ❤️ if you believe in the power of the heart .

Alma … the soul …. The name of our 6 day retreat .

Words can not nor will not ever be able to describe the depths of growth and transformation that ocurres this week in our Final retreat of the year .
Guests joined us from as far as Switzerland with open hearts and as a result ….
Mother Ayahuasca showed up in a Big way , healed bodies , transformed hearts healed deep wounds … and transformed lives .

It was my deepest honor to be able to serve you all this week and host you in Colombia which now holds a special place in all of our Hearts .

A special thank you to the WONDERFUL staff at @playakoralia … we consider you now a part of our family , and look forward to 4 more retreats next year :)

Hay algunas heridas, hay algo de Miedo, pero te PROMETO que todo eso se puede sanar.

node.text:
Leave a ❤️❤️❤️ if you felt this .

My beautiful sister …. You are perfect EXACTLY the way you are 🙏🏼✨

The world has worked hard to convince you there’s something you have to change in order to find yourself …. To find Love.

Yet there’s nothing to change , nothing to FIND… for YOU are LOVE…. the purest essence of it 

Your magic is INSIDE… 
it’s in your intuition 
in your knowing
its in your ability to create Life 
Your ability to love unconditionally
Your ability to heal with a smile,
With a touch 
its in your heart ❤️ 

You’re perfect exactly the way you are .
You have been since the moment you were born and when you discover this …. we all do .

When you remember we will all remember
When you awaken … we will all awaken 
When you Heal …. We will all Heal 🙏🏼✨

node.text:
Leave a 🙏🏼 if you felt this .

I remember my first spiritual experience like it was yesterday … it was a short 2 years ago . 

Prior to then I was arrogant , competitive, materialistic , aggressive , cut throat …. Honestly I was an ass 🤷🏻‍♂️🤦🏻‍♂️😂

I always meant well , always wanted to help others … yet I had so much pain inside that I wasn’t aware of because I had been living with it so long I thought it was “ME”

Slowly , after every experience my heart started to open, my mind started to let go … and my awakening and healing took place .

I say both words , because when you heal … you Awaken .  When you Awaken , you see how beautiful Life really is , and how abundant YOU really are .

I’ve had …. Probably 50-60 experiences since then , and the man you see and more importantly FEEL today … is a result of all those experiences , a result of me drawing closer to Source , Oneness and Love .

What was your first  experience like what did it feel like and what did you see ?

Deje un 🙏🏼 si sentisteis esto.

Recuerdo mi primera experiencia espiritual como si fuera ayer ... fue hace unos 2 años.

Antes de eso, era arrogante, competitivo, materialista, agresivo, degollado…. Honestamente era terrible jajaja

Siempre tuve buenas intenciones, siempre quise ayudar a los demás ... sin embargo, tenía tanto dolor por dentro del que no era consciente porque había estado viviendo con él durante tanto tiempo que pensaba que ese dolor era "YO"

Lentamente, después de cada experiencia, mi corazón comenzó a abrirse, mi mente comenzó a soltarse ... y mi despertar y mi sanción tuvieron lugar.

Digo ambas palabras, porque cuando sanas ... despiertas.  Cuando despiertas, ves lo hermosa que es realmente la vida y lo abundante que eres en realidad.

He tenido …. Probablemente 50-60 experiences así desde entonces, y el hombre que ves y SIENTES en mi hoy ... es el resultado de todas esas experiencias, un resultado de mi acercamiento a la Fuente, la Unidad y el Amor.

 ¿Cuál fue su primera experiencia espiritual? ¿Cómo se sintió y qué vio?

Drop a YES if you're ready to tap into your PERSONAL POWER! 👇

These two things , right here when done DAILY will change your LIFE.  They allow you to connect with yourself, connect with nature, and disconnect from all the noise out there.

The choice is yours ... you have the power within. It's time to start EMPOWERING it ... and allowing it to SHINE.

If you're up for the challenge , Finish the rest of the month doing these two things DAILY... and tag a friend or 2 you'd like to team up with to do them with BELOW! 👇

¡Dejad un SÍ si está listo para acceder a su PODER PERSONAL! 👇

Estas dos cosas, aquí, cuando se hace a diario, cambiarán tu vida. Te permiten conectarte contigo mismo, conectarte con la naturaleza y desconectar de todo el ruido que hay ahí fuera.

La elección es tuya ... tienes el poder interior. Es hora de empezar a empoderarlo ... y permitir que brille.

Si estás a la altura del desafío, termina el resto del mes haciendo estas dos cosas a diario... y etiqueta a un amigo o 2 con el que te gustaría trabajar para hacerlas con abajo! 👇

node.text:
Leave a ✨✨ if YOU have COURAGE within

It takes Courage , because living the way you’ve always known … is comfortable . Living the life of your dreams … requires healing , vision and courage 

Yet healing requires FEELING, the thing most of us want to avoid , yet the key to true inner peace 

The greatest source of healing comes when you tap into the 5th dimension.

When you go past All feeling , all thought and connect direct to Source ….. direct to YOU .

Connect to the feelings , the hurt and simply …. Let them all go, shed those layers and get closer to revealing and feeling the heart .

Once the heart reopens , you become a Magnet for all the desires of your heart …. Struggle ceases , and flow replaces it.

It’s a beautiful process of transformation … the same that a butterfly goes through thus … our logo

You can do this … with no outside substance … just you and the tools God has given you . Just requires a little guidance 

It’s beautiful and we will be taking you through 6 life changing experiences like this at AWAKEN  in November .( link in bio) 

I’ll look forward to guiding you through , your very own Healing process 🙏🏼

Deja un ✨✨ si eres valiente

La mayor fuente de sanación llega cuando accedes a la quinta dimensión.

Cuando pasas todo sentimiento, todo pensamiento y te conectas directamente a la Fuente ... directamente a TI.

Puedes hacer esto ... sin sustancia externa ... solo tú y las herramientas que Dios te ha dado.  Solo requiere un poco de orientación

 Es hermoso y lo llevaremos a través de 6 experiencias que cambian vidas como esta en AWAKEN en noviembre. (Enlace en mi perfil )

Espero poder guiarte a través de tu propio proceso de sanacion🙏🏼
